libs.content:
find_library(o2_library_static names libo2.a libo2_static.a o2_static
    paths
    /usr/local/lib
    /usr/lib
    "$env{lib_dir}/lib"
    "$env{lib}"
    )

find_library(spatialindex_library names spatialindex_i spatialindex spatialindex-64 paths
  /usr/lib
  /usr/local/lib
  "$env{lib_dir}/lib"
  "$env{lib}/lib"
  "$env{osgeo4w_root}/lib"
  )

find_program(odbc_config
    names odbc_config iodbc-config
    doc "path to unixodbc or iodbc config program")

find_library(postgres_library names pq libpq libpqdll paths 
      /usr/local/lib 
      /usr/lib 
      c:/msys/local/lib
      "$env{lib_dir}/lib"
      )
find_library(postgres_library names pq libpq libpqdll paths ${pg_tmp}/lib)

  "$env{lib_dir}/lib"
  c:/msys/local/lib
  no_default_path
  )

  "$env{lib_dir}/lib"

  no_default_path
  )

  )

  "$env{lib}/lib"
  no_default_path
)
